paragraphs.body: As a voice artist, Buescher is known for many roles, including Anko Mitarashi on Naruto. She is also a skilled puppeteer and has worked for both Sesame Street and The Muppets. Buescher recently received an offer to join the cast of Avenue Q; she can also be heard as the announcer for E!'s The Soup, Gone Bad, and Love Chai. Buescher was a member of The Second City comedy troupe.

paragraphs.body: Buescher is a breast cancer survivor and is supportive of attempts to raise awareness of the issue, having written about her own experiences and produced an award winning film on the subject.
